HEADWORD: Oleometer
<hw>O`le*om`e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>oleum</ets> oil + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
